Interface StreamedHttpResponse

All Superinterfaces:
io.netty.handler.codec.DecoderResultProvider, io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpMessage, io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpObject, io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpResponse, Publisher<io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpContent>, StreamedHttpMessage
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultStreamedHttpResponse, DelegateStreamedHttpResponse
public interface StreamedHttpResponse extends io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpResponse, StreamedHttpMessage
Combines HttpResponse and StreamedHttpMessage into one message. So it represents a http response with a stream of HttpContent messages that can be subscribed to.
